<abstract><t>In Ethernet based aggregation networks, several subscriber premises may be logically connected to the same interface of an edge router. This document proposes a method for the edge router to identify the subscriber premises using the contents of the received Router Solicitation messages.  The applicability is limited to the N:1 VLAN allocation model.</t></abstract>

